      "solution": "import math\nnum = int(input())\nif num % 2 == 1:\n    if round(math.cbrt(num), 2) == int(math.cbrt(num)):\n        print(int(math.cbrt(num)))\n    else:\n        print(-1)\nelse:\n    if round(math.sqrt(num), 2) == int(math.sqrt(num)):\n        print(int(math.sqrt(num)))\n    else:\n        print(-1)\n",
