    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">Find the cube or square root of a number <var>n</var>.<br>If the given number is odd, output the cube root.<br>But if the given number is even, output the square root.<br>If the square root of an even <var>n</var> or a cube root of an odd <var>n</var> is not an integer, output <const>-1</const>.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>line 1</strong>: an integer <var>n</var>.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\"><strong>1 line</strong>: either the cube root of <var>n</var>, square root of <var>n</var>, or <const>-1</const>.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &lt;= <var>n</var> &lt;= 1000000</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">1</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">1</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
